News Corp. (NWSA)  and  Exor SpA (EXO)  are working on
a joint bid for Formula One, Sky News reported, without saying
where it got the information.  Formula One is owned by CVC Capital Partners Ltd., a
London-based private equity company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
